  6 DISCUSSION
  6.1 Different Subchord Features
  In the model presented in this paper, the subchord features
  coincide with the chords and emission distributions are dis-
  crete. This is not generally necessary, and one could well
  imagine trying out different sets of features, be they based
  on chromagrams or not. Advances in multi-pitch estima-
