  The separation ofWintoHandPis a kind of under-
  determined blind source separation problem. One way to
  mathematically formulate this kind of problems is putting
  it on MAP (Maximum A Posteriori) estimation framework
  through representing desired source properties as a priori
  probabilities. Assuming thatHandPare independent, the
