  4
  Comparing the entropy values given by the GHSOM ap-
  proach to the ones presented in \[8\] reveals that the GH-
  SOM approach performs very similar to the SOM-based ap-
  proach followed in \[8\]. This is obviously no surprise, but
  shows that the automated splitting of clusters by the GH-
  SOM does not harm the entropy of the generated playlists,
  while at the same time offers the additional benefit of auto-
  matically structuring the created playlists in a hierarchical
  manner. Like those created by the recursive SOM approach
  in \[8\], the GHSOM-based playlists show quite good long-
  term entropy values (for large values ofn), but rather poor
  values for short playlists.
