  (Figure 5) changing his SPM. First, he ran at 80SPM and
  when music was played, he started to run at 120SPM. When
  the music changed, he started to run again at 80SPM. He
  repeated this until the music changed nine times. He also
  ran at 80 - 160SPM, 120 - 160SPM, and 120 - 200SPM.
