  A ROBOT SINGER WITH MUSIC RECOGNITION
  BASED ON REAL-TIME BEAT TRACKING
  Kazumasa Murata
  †
  , Kazuhiro Nakadai
  ‡,†
  , Kazuyoshi Yoshii
