  2.2 Retrieval
  With the main goal of efficiency, continuing the parallel with
  textual information retrieval techniques, retrieval is carried
  out using thebag of wordsparadigm. Thus the similarity be-
  tween the query and the recordings in the collection is car-
  ried out by simply counting the number of hashes of quan-
