  ISMIR 2008 – Session 3a – Content-Based Retrieval, Categorization and Similarity 1
  (MRR) of90.2, which is significantly higher than MRR for
  the pure HMM-based approach. Moreover, for the complete
  approach, every query gives the correct work ranked among
  the first10positions, which is an important result for many
  of the applications of supervised music identification that
  have been described in Section 1.
