  γ\[8\]:\
  α∼gamma(1,0.1),γ∼gamma(1,0.1)(2)\
  and learn them during inference. For the priorHoverφ,\
  we use the normal-inverse-Wishart distribution \[12\] with pa-\
  rametersκ\
