  rock,R&B,punk and so on.The number of paragraphs\
  in the lyrics for each song of this set varies from 5 to 27.\
  Table 3 displays more specific information about the songs\
  in the test bed.Because the algorithm proposed in this pa-\
  per has been designed to obtain paragraph-to-segment align-\
  ment,we have evaluated the alignment accuracy by compar-\
