  (T).\
  Under this representation,the total luminance of the origi-\
  nal image and the binarized image is identical.Thus,one\
  can minimize the cross-entropy between the two images,\
  or equivalently,minimize the Kullback-Leibler (KL) diver-\
  gence,by minimizing\
