  Rather than identifying incorrect mappings, one may also\
  increase the number of correct identifications. For this, cer-\
  tain tuples are specified as true positives by “filling” small\
  gaps within horizontal line segments. Thus, OMR queries\
  are assigned to a specific audio document if neighboring\
