  dition of sources for Matlab and Octave bindings (mex) that\
  allow access to data stored in SDIF files for these two pro-\
  graming environments. The Matlab/Octave interface makes\
  use of the frame and matrix header cache of Easdif to allow\
  efficient random access to SDIF frames and matrices.\
  Additionally, the Easdif library includes support for the\
  SWIG\
