  3.3. Critical bands\
  Grouping frequency bins into critical bands is a\
  psychoacoustically motivated principle. In \[11\], 36 bands\
  of triangular-response bandwidth were used along the\
  critical bands, and power in each band was used to derive\
  a detection function. Detection functions based on equal-\
  loudness changes in Equivalent Rectangular Bandwidth\
  (ERB) bands have also been used in the past \[8\]:\
