  process is a series of onset locations denoting the time\
  points at which an onset has occurred.\
  6\. EXPERIMENTAL RESULTS\
  6.1. Database Description\
  Our database consists of 18 singing recordings of pop\
  songs, from 4 singers (2 male, 2 female) of varied singing\
  styles. The pieces were annotated by hand for onsets, and\
  contained a total of 1127 onsets. Approximately half\
