  there shall be exactly one basis vector per midi pitch\
  and in a single training instance there is only one tone\
  present. The values ofHare set to the corresponding\
  values of the amplitude envelope expressing the current\
  loudness of the sound. Then the tone model is calcu-\
  lated as described in section 2.3 but having a fixedH\
