  6 DISCUSSION AND FUTURE WORK\
  While an inverse relationship between Earth Mover’s Dis-\
  tance and the maximum flow value might be expected on the\
  basis of the conventional wisdom that a community of artists\
  tend to be somehow aurally similar, this does not appear to\
  be strictly the case. The evidence, at least in this sample set,\
  does not support this relationship, though it doesn’t disprove\
  it either. However, based upon the difference in result from\
  the Kruskal-Wallis one-way ANOVA test and simple obser-\
