  representation, we apply it to the classification task of genre
  recognition. As classifier, we use the AdaBoost meta-learning
  algorithm. This choice is motivated by the fact that source
  code \[8\] is available as well as published results for a set
  of genre recognition experiments \[1\]. Those experiments
