  long musical audio signals, we can reduce memory space
  by splitting a large self-similarity matrix into multiple sub-
  matrices with comparatively small size along the diagonal
  (Fig. 4). This causes few problems because the left lower
  and right upper parts of the matrix rarely match with a query
  matrix. To avoid degradation around the boundaries of the
