  of the same style.
  It is clear from this experiment that the TRAP-TANDEM
  features are more reliable than the short-term spectral shape
  features in a music retrieval context. It is worth noticing that
  MFCCs with a simple average and cosine similarity leads
  to poorer results than MFCCs with mean, full covariance
  matrix and KL divergence, while for the TRAP-TANDEM
  features, the use of a KL-based distance function leads to
  slightly inferior results than the simpler cosine similarity.
