  stalled (http://www.rmcpickup.com/polydriveii.html) that
  was connected to a Roland GR-33 guitar synthesizer responsible for the
  pitch to MIDI conversion (http://www.roland.com/products/
  en/GR-33/index.html).
  performed the following songs:Bim Bom,O Barquinho,In-
  sensatez(How Insensitive),Garota de Ipanema(Girl from
  Ipanema),S
