   ̃
  ao Gilberto plays? In the
  literature we were able to find several transcriptions of pat-
  terns played by Jo
   ̃
  ao Gilberto \[4, 9\]. So, we have built a
  catalogue containing 21 different patterns (labeled P1, P2,
  etc.), all manually transcribed by musicologists from Jo
   ̃
  ao
  Gilberto’s recordings. Examples of patterns in this cata-
  logue are showed in Figure 3.
