  is, we used the algorithm without any sort of modifica-
  tions and/or adaptations. Although the algorithm found pat-
  terns from the catalogue, including patterns with some small
  modifications, the results, in this case, were not so good as
  we previously expected. Table 1 summarizes the results we
  obtained with FlExPat.
