  3.2 Beat tracking
  For the estimation of beat times from the band-wise onset
  signals an algorithm based on the method proposed by Kla-
  puri et al. in \[2\] has been used. The algorithm had to be
  adapted to the type of onset signals that are obtained using
  the phase slope function. This modified beat tracker will be
  referred to as M-KLAP in the rest of the paper. Experiments
  for the development of M-KLAP have been conducted using
  the music data set, D2, described in Section 3.1.
