  that part in the near future.
  5 CONCLUSIONS
  In this paper a new method to detect onsets using the av-
  erage of the group delay was introduced and evaluated in a
  beat tracking framework. Advantages are the immediate de-
  tection of the onsets by locating the positive zero crossings
  of the phase slope, and the robustness for signals with little
  percussive content as shown in the experiments. The next
  steps to improve the method are a more efficient implemen-
  tation of the phase slope computation and refinements of the
  beat tracker. Also, evaluation on different data sets of folk
  music will be performed.
