  For the remainder of this paper, we will assume that the
  ground distance for the EMD is the Euclidean metricl
  2
  .
  With this assumption in mind, we drop the subscript re-
  ferring to the ground distance from our formulas, writing
  EMD(A, B)instead ofEMD
