  There are several ways to assess the fitness of a feature.
  We follow here a wrapper approach \[6\], by which features
  are evaluated using a classifier built on-the-fly during the
  feature search process \[14\]. The fitness of the feature is
  defined as the performance of a classifier built with this
  unique feature.
