  6. RESULTS
  
  6.1 Individual Feature Search
  
  To assess the search performance of IFS we compare it
  against the search performance of a standard genetic algorithm on three audio classification problems. These problems are the same presented in the section 3. The genetic
  algorithm we use is described in \[14\].
